comments.message:
can we name this message something more specific? The Firmware page is a good example on how to structure messages 

Example: 

"modal" : {
  "resetConfirm": { 
     "message1": "...."
     "message2": "...."
     "message3": "...."
 }
}

or 
"modal" : {
   "resetConfirmMessage1": "...."
   "resetConfirmMessage2": "...."
   "resetConfirmMessage3": "...."
}
